First I want to thank Apachii for permission to use her mod which is necessary for this mod to work...  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

Screenshot uses Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE V2-V3 Armor Replacer -Work In Progress- by Killer Keo http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3654

I think I have made Uthgerd the Unbroken an attractive woman.  I know there are a bazillion of these mods for her, but this is one that I made for my own use and thought I would distribute it.
